---

<section id="health-management" class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-cyan-50/20 to-tiffany-50/30">
  <div class="section-container">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-20 fade-in">
      <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-tiffany-100 rounded-full text-tiffany-700 font-medium text-sm mb-6">
        時代の転換点
      </div>
      <h2 class="heading-section mb-6">
        「やりっぱなし健診」からの脱却。<br />
        時代は <span class="text-gradient">「健康経営3.0」</span> へ。
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Comparison Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-20">
      <!-- Old Way (1.0) -->
      <div class="slide-up">
        <div class="relative p-10 bg-neutral-50 rounded-3xl border-2 border-neutral-200">
          <!-- Badge -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-8 px-6 py-2 bg-neutral-400 rounded-full text-white font-semibold text-sm">
            従来の健康経営 1.0
          </div>

          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-neutral-200 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 mt-4">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-neutral-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>

          <!-- Problems -->
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-1">義務としての年1回の健診</div>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">やりっぱなし健診、ほったらかし健診</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-1">コストに見合う利益が創出されていない</div>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">投資対効果が不明確</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-1">行動変容につながらない</div>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">受動的な健康管理</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Transformation Arrow (Desktop) -->
      <div class="hidden lg:flex absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-tiffany rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-luxury-lg animate-pulse">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 px-6 py-2 bg-white rounded-full shadow-luxury border-2 border-tiffany-500">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-tiffany-700">TRANSFORMATION</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- New Way (3.0) -->
      <div class="slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <div class="relative p-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-tiffany-50 to-white rounded-3xl border-2 border-tiffany-300 shadow-luxury">
          <!-- Badge -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-8 px-6 py-2 bg-gradient-tiffany rounded-full text-white font-semibold text-sm shadow-luxury">
            これからの健康経営 3.0
          </div>

          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-tiffany rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 mt-4 shadow-luxury">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>

          <!-- Benefits -->
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-tiffany-100 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-tiffany-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-1">
                  <span class="text-tiffany-700">ワークエンゲージメント</span>と<span class="text-tiffany-700">ヘルスエンゲージメント</span>の両立
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">能動的な健康投資</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-tiffany-100 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-tiffany-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-1">定年は <span class="text-tiffany-700">「健康年齢」</span> で決める社会へ</div>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">年齢ではなく健康状態で</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-tiffany-100 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-tiffany-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-1">
                  高い自己管理能力を持つ<span class="text-tiffany-700">生涯現役従業員</span>の育成
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">自律的な健康管理</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-tiffany-100 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-tiffany-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-1">
                  AIモニタリングによる<span class="text-tiffany-700">個別最適化プラン</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">データドリブンな健康管理</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-tiffany-100 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-tiffany-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-1">
                  リスク因子（高血圧・糖尿病・肥満）の<span class="text-tiffany-700">早期管理</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">予防的介入</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Key Message -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
      <div class="card-luxury">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-tiffany rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-luxury">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-sans font-bold text-neutral-900">
            健康経営3.0への第一歩を、ここから。
          </h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-body mb-8">
          従業員の健康を「コスト」から「投資」へ。<br />
          データとテクノロジーで実現する、新しい健康経営のカタチ。
        </p>
        <a href="#platform" class="btn-primary inline-flex">
          プラットフォームを見る
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
